description: This file serves as the entry point for a React frontend application. It imports necessary React dependencies, including React, ReactDOM, CSS styles, and the main App component. It initializes the React rendering process by creating a root and rendering the App component within StrictMode.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root for rendering React components into the DOM.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree into the DOM root.
